 <item> <title>Education Department Announces School Improvement Grants for 16 States</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/news/press-releases/education-department-announces-school-improvement-grants-16-states</link>
 <description>The U.S. Department of Education announced today that 16 states will receive more than $113 million in grants to continue efforts to turn around our nation&#039;s persistently lowest-achieving schools through awards from the Department&#039;s School Improvement Grants (SIG) program.</description>
